{
  "id": "restart-event-53-recall-ambulance-siren",
  "name": "追索事件：召回救护车鸣笛",
  "description": "护送队名单刚成形，旧救护车从站外雾里倒车回来。车门上的字不是“急救”，而是“召回”。它要把刚离院的活证人送回 Ward Zero 复核。",
  "trigger": {"condition": true},
  "conditions": [
    "flag.restart_escort_gallery_roster_signed:1",
    "NOT:flag.restart_recall_ambulance_answered:1"
  ],
  "consequences": ["restart-recall-ambulance-diverted"],
  "options": [
    {
      "text": "把活人出院通行证贴到车门上，逼救护车承认这次不是入院运输，而是院外送达。",
      "effects": [
        "gain.influence:18",
        "set.flag:restart_recall_ambulance_answered",
        "set.flag:restart_ambulance_converted_to_escort_transfer"
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "让塔内播音员的活人声线盖过鸣笛，把召回指令改成无法定位的静电回执。",
      "effects": [
        "gain.favor:18",
        "set.flag:restart_recall_ambulance_answered",
        "set.flag:restart_operator_jammed_recall_siren"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
